      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is best suited for someone looking for a functional daily driver at an accessible price point. The exterior shows some age with noticeable scratches and minor dings, and the interior upholstery exhibits visible wear from regular use. While the car starts and runs reliably, it will likely need upcoming maintenance for items like brake pads and potentially a new set of tires soon. It is a solid, honest vehicle that has served its previous owner well but is no longer in peak aesthetic or mechanical form.",
