    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s been well-loved and is ready for more adventures? I\u2019m parting ways with my car, and it's in really nice shape! It drives super smoothly and has been a total joy to own. Whether you're commuting to work or heading out for a weekend getaway, this car is ready to go. It\u2019s been well-maintained and is just waiting for someone new to take the wheel. Come check it out\u2014you\u2019re going to love how it feels on the road!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
