      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This 2002 Porsche 911 Carrera (996.2) features the 3.6L M96 flat-six powerplant, delivering 320 hp through a crisp 6-speed G96 manual transaxle. The vehicle maintains excellent mechanical integrity, featuring a documented IMS bearing retrofit and rear main seal replacement. The Variocam Plus system ensures a linear power band and aggressive throttle response up to the 7,200 RPM redline. Its chassis remains sharp, utilizing MacPherson struts and a multi-link rear setup that provides the communicative feedback synonymous with the 911 lineage. While showing minor aesthetic patina consistent with a well-loved driver, the engine exhibits strong compression and a clean DME report. A purist-spec example ready for the technical curves of a backroad.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_3",
