      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E92 M3 featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8. This power plant utilizes individual throttle bodies to deliver 414 hp with an 8,400 RPM redline, paired to a precise 6-speed manual transmission. The chassis benefits from the M Variable Differential Lock and a carbon fiber reinforced plastic (CFRP) roof for optimized weight distribution. Recent preventative maintenance includes updated rod bearings and throttle actuators. The suspension geometry remains true with no bushing play, though the exterior shows minor stone chips consistent with road use. A mechanically robust specimen for the purist enthusiast.",
